<div class="case-study"><h3>In Practice</h3><p>A technology company came to us after a frustrating year with a traditional SEO agency. Rankings had improved, but pipeline hadn't. Their CMO described the problem clearly: "We're winning on Google, but losing to AI." Within two quarters, AI had become a measurable source of inbound pipeline attribution — a result their previous agency's model was structurally incapable of producing.</p></div></section>
